description:
This week, ANN features several stories, including the 2023 Adventist Church Ten Days of Prayer initiative, the work of an Adventist pastor helping families living in Ukraine, a woman’s commitment to evangelism, and a look at the Adventist school for the Deaf in Kenya. 

For more Adventist news, subscribe to our Youtube channel. 

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. For all things Adventist news, visit adventist.news
